o You for I have certainly been among the wrongdoers,'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34730,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/seeks-refuge-end-of-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":38167,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet seeks refuge at the end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to seek refuge from these at the end of prayer, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from cowardice. I seek refuge in You from returning to the feebleness of old age. I seek\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5952,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/06\/none-say-muhammad-better-yunus\/","url_meta":{"origin":38167,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Yunus: None should say Muhammad better than Jonah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant should say that I am better than Jonah son of Mata.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"Whoever says that I am better than Jonah son of Mata has told a lie.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3234,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &q